============================================================
  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Hubble's Law
Formula: v = H₀ × d
Note:    Universe is expanding; galaxies recede from us

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   DNA Structure
Formula: Double helix; A-T and G-C base pairs
Note:    Stores and transmits genetic information

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Bayes Theorem
Formula: P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)
Note:    Updating probability based on new evidence

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   pH Definition
Formula: pH = -log[H+]
Note:    Measure of hydrogen ion concentration; 7 is neutral

